So, adrian,
how have you been?

03:10.300 --> 03:11.300
You look great.

03:11.300 --> 03:12.667
- thank you.

03:12.667 --> 03:14.334
Do you remember the name
of that establishment,

03:14.334 --> 03:15.367
The other cleaners?

03:15.367 --> 03:16.634
- no, i don't remember

03:16.634 --> 03:17.901
- do you have the ticket?

03:17.901 --> 03:20.501
I know, you always--
you always, um,

03:20.501 --> 03:24.567
You know, put the tickets
in your purse.

